com.chute.sdk.v2.model

Class AssetModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chute.sdk.v2.model.AssetModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class AssetModel
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    An asset represents a single media item and all information connected to it, viewed by everyone or privileged users. Each asset consists of links, thumbnail, URL, type, caption, dimensions, source and the user which the asset belongs to.
